    Demo -.->|validates| OS
    D_UIF -.->|CLI dead-end fallback| Demo

    Meta -.->|authoring contract and weekly refresh| Industry
    Meta -.->|authoring contract and weekly refresh| Generic
    Meta -.->|authoring contract and weekly refresh| Core

